OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The far-right Italian party Brothers of
OL,6, Italy, tipped to win Sunday's election,
OL,7, has suspended one of its candidates for
OL,8, praising Adolf Hitler on social media. 
OL,10,FIn a 2014 Facebook post Calogero       
OL,11,FPisano, a party co-ordinator in        
OL,12,FAgrigento in Sicily, compared leader   
OL,13,FGiorgia Meloni to "a great statesman of
OL,14,F70 years ago".                         
OL,16,FHe added that he was referring to a    
OL,17,F"German" and not Benito Mussolini.     
OL,19,FThe party said Mr Pisano no longer     
OL,20,Frepresented it at any level.           
